A: You can use the nextToken() method of StringTokenizer to read the next token from the string.
StringTokenizer st = new StringTokenizer("2 4 5 6 1 3 8 2 8");
while (st.hasMoreTokens()) {
    String token = st.nextToken();
    System.out.println(token);
}

